project.description:
There are multiple projects that we work on.

- We make a membership system, which is released. It is used in production for our non-profit organization.
- We are working on an event management system where you can invite people to events and give access to the venues on current signups.

Klynge is a non-profit organization working to improve welfare and quality of life; we do that through networking events, having people share their experiences, mentoring others and building relationships. Everything we build is released Open Source, most notably our membership system.
